      • process

        public void process(SeriesDataWritable series)
        Processes the whole series, looking for nodules. Uses the correlational method for detecting nodules. By this, it checks if two nodule candidates in adjacent slices may actually be part of the same nodule.
        Parameters:
        series -

      • validateNodules

        public void validateNodules()
